    narr:childCount "48"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "c6887c215ba704fe80f789957cbfc95d4a1a57af" ;
    narr:narration """The authoritative register of aswritten.ai is defined by a [deliberate, agent-first voice](narr:StyleObs_ActiveVoice) that treats [epistemological terms](narr:StyleObs_EpistemologicalRegister) as precise technical constraints. The narrative trajectory has evolved from [early imperative workflow lists](narr:StyleObs_BulletedDecisionLists) toward a [sectioned analytical voice](narr:StyleObs_SectionedNarrativeVoice) that balances [block-quoted founder corrections](narr:StyleObs_BlockquoteCorrections) with [epistemic precision](narr:Style_EpistemicPrecision) to distinguish between mere 'leaning' and firm 'decision.' The system consistently frames itself as [its own first user](narr:StyleObs_FirstUserPositioning), a thesis governing how it handles [customer CTO guardrails](narr:StyleObs_CustomerCTOGuardPullRequests_Imperative) and [enterprise pilot validation](narr:StyleObs_EnterpriseCustomerPattern_Tone). Architectural finality is signaled through [short, punchy declarative sentences](narr:StyleObs_ShortPunchyCadence) and [emphatic ALL-CAPS](narr:StyleObs_AllCapsEmphasis), specifically a recurring [ALL-CAPS 'IS'](narr:StyleObs_AllCapsIS). The register remains highly self-aware, employing [antithetical definitions](narr:StyleObs_8) and [inline deprecation](narr:StyleObs_3) to maintain a clean, actionable knowledge graph.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_10> ;
